          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">My Tri-athlete from "'The Lovely Life of Arnold" <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue10/martin_goodman/bio.php" class="link3">Martin Goodman</a></span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
